OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,FEthnic minority communities in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland are still "living in
OL,8,Ffear" one month on from race riots
OL,9,Fwhich saw children having to be
OL,10,Frescued from their homes, a senior
OL,11,Fpolice officer has said.
OL,13,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,14,F(PSNI) Assistant Chief Constable Davy
OL,15,FBeck also told MPs that a man charged
OL,16,Fover a stabbing which preceded the
OL,17,Fviolence may be from Chad, and not
OL,18,FSudan as previously believed.
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
