CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,FViolence flared in several areas in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland in June after a
OL,8,Fgraphic video clip emerged of a man
OL,9,Fbeing stabbed in north Belfast.
OL,11,FThe victim, Stephen Ogilvie, who is
OL,12,Faged in his 40s, lost his left eye in
OL,13,Fthe attack and also sustained deep
OL,14,Fwounds to his head, face and back.
OL,16,FFollowing the attack, Hadi Alodid, 30,
OL,17,Fappeared at Belfast Magistrates' Court
OL,18,Fcharged with attempted murder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,FThe disorder following the stabbing
OL,7,Fsaw masked mobs set fire to homes,
OL,8,Fcars and a bus, with people targeted
OL,9,Fbased on their race.
OL,11,FForeign national healthcare workers
OL,12,Fwere also subjected to threats and
OL,13,Fintimidation.
OL,15,FMr Beck appeared before a joint
OL,16,Fsitting of the Home Affairs and
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland Affairs Committees to
OL,18,Fprovide an update.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,FHe told MPs: "This was the third year
OL,7,Fin a row that we in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fhave witnessed what I could only
OL,9,Fdescribe as atrocious violence and
OL,10,Fracism that impacted many of our
OL,11,Fcommunities, who are still very much
OL,12,Freeling from what was experienced."
OL,14,FIn the immediate aftermath of the
OL,15,Fknife attack, the PSNI had said the
OL,16,Fsuspect was believed to be Somalian
OL,17,Fbefore later stating that he was
OL,18,FSudanese.
OL,26,@nD@NOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,FMr Beck told the committees: "Our
OL,7,Finquiries would indicate that the male
OL,8,Fsuspect entered Northern Ireland via
OL,9,Fthe Common Travel Area in February
OL,10,F2023 and was subsequently granted
OL,11,Fleave to remain in UK until 2028.
OL,13,F"We do continue to investigate the
OL,14,Forigins of the male with one potential
OL,15,Fline of inquiry indicating that he may
OL,16,Fpotentially be from Chad and not
OL,17,FSudan, as was initially indicated, and
OL,18,Fwe continue to investigate that line
OL,19,Fof inquiry with the relevant
OL,20,Fauthorities in Chad."
OL,26,@nD@^OUuD@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,FThe senior officer said following the
OL,7,Fstabbing attack, police became aware
OL,8,F"of significant online calls for
OL,9,Fprotests at sites across Northern
OL,10,FIreland".
OL,12,FHe said: "These calls, I would say,
OL,13,Fhad a clear anti-immigration and
OL,14,Fextreme right-wing theme.
OL,16,F"There were also significant calls for
OL,17,Fpeople to come prepared for disorder.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@HO]tD@JOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,F"People were instructed, for example,
OL,7,Fto wear masks, to dress in black, and
OL,8,Fleave their electronic devices at
OL,9,Fhome, we believe in an attempt to
OL,10,Ffrustrate police subsequent
OL,11,Finvestigations."
OL,13,FHe added: "We then saw on June 9
OL,14,Freally serious, sustained, and what I
OL,15,Fwould describe as racially motivated
OL,16,Fdisorder across Northern Ireland.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@PO]uD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,F"Groups, mainly men, blocked roads,
OL,7,Fset fire to vehicles, and went street
OL,8,Fto street, destroying property and
OL,9,Fattacking the homes that they believed
OL,10,Fto belong to ethnic minorities.
OL,12,F"This was some of the most serious
OL,13,Fdisorder and violence we have seen in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland for many years, and I
OL,15,Fwould have to say that had it not been
OL,16,Ffor the response of police, supported,
OL,17,FI would say by colleagues from Fire
OL,18,Fand Rescue Service and the Ambulance
OL,19,FService, I have no doubt that lives
OL,20,Fcould well have been lost on that
OL,21,Fnight."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,FMr Beck said officers had rescued
OL,7,Fchildren aged six and eight from one
OL,8,Fhouse where their father had attempted
OL,9,Fto hide them and in another incident,
OL,10,Fa two-month-old baby was rescued by
OL,11,Femergency services.
OL,13,FHe said the violence had continued
OL,14,Finto a second evening but it was "more
OL,15,Flocalised".
OL,26,@vD@bOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,FThe officer told the committees: "This
OL,7,Fdisorder was conducted by what I would
OL,8,Fdescribe as thugs, and they were
OL,9,Fresponsible for targeting people
OL,10,Fsimply because they perceived them not
OL,11,Fto be white.
OL,13,F"Many of those attacked have been
OL,14,Fresident in Northern Ireland for many
OL,15,Fyears, and in some cases their entire
OL,16,Flives, and many are key workers in our
OL,17,Fhealth service, and they contribute
OL,18,Fsignificantly to society, much more
OL,19,Fthan the mindless thugs who targeted
OL,20,Fthem."
OL,26,@nD@bOUuD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,FMr Beck said 49 PSNI officers were
OL,7,Finjured during the rioting and that
OL,8,F168 police officers were seconded from
OL,9,Fother UK police forces to assist.
OL,11,FHe said a "significant investigation
OL,12,Fteam" was probing the disorder and
OL,13,Fpolice have made 35 arrests with 27
OL,14,Fcharged directly to court.
OL,26,@sD@KOUtD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,FHe added: "In addition to responding
OL,7,Fto the disorder, we put significant
OL,8,Ftime and effort into engaging with our
OL,9,Fethnic minority communities across
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland, and indeed have
OL,11,Fpersonally spoken to a number of
OL,12,Frepresentatives from these communities.
OL,14,F"I would say that these communities
OL,15,Fare still very much living in fear,
OL,16,Fpeople are afraid to go about their
OL,17,Fdaily activity.
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,F"We have seen racist criminal damage,
OL,7,Fassaults, and threats continue in
OL,8,Fparts of the country, and so clearly
OL,9,Ftensions remain high at this stage,
OL,10,Fand we continue to see and remove
OL,11,Fracist material across a number of
OL,12,Flocations."
OL,14,FThe senior officer said members of
OL,15,Floyalist paramilitary groups were
OL,16,Fpresent at some sites during the
OL,17,Fdisorder and were "involved in
OL,18,Fdirecting the violence at a number of
OL,19,Flocations".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@KO]yD@SOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a review has found that
OL,7,FPSNI use of water cannon and baton
OL,8,Frounds during the widespread rioting
OL,9,Fin June was "proportionate".
OL,11,FThe Police Ombudsman has carried out a
OL,12,Freview into the police use of force
OL,13,Fduring the disorder.
OL,15,FThe ombudsman reviewed police use of
OL,16,Fwater cannon and attenuating energy
OL,17,Fprojectiles (AEPs), commonly known as
OL,18,Fbaton rounds, and concluded their use
OL,19,Fwas proportionate.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783669804
OL,3,CEthnic minority communities in NI
OL,4,Cstill 'living in fear' after June riots
OL,6,FPolice used AEPs 20 times, along with
OL,7,Fwater cannon, to help control disorder
OL,8,Fon the night of June 10.
OL,10,FBody-worn video footage of the
OL,11,Fincidents was subsequently assessed by
OL,12,FPolice Ombudsman investigators.
OL,14,FAEPs were used 15 times in Glengormley
OL,15,Fand five times in Portadown.
